title: Riverside - Stuck Between (Dutch Treat ^B070 Symphonic Rock)
description:
I stumbled upon a track called: Deprived. And indeed I was (a long time). Riverside is a band from Warsaw and sounds like Porcupine Tree. A big surprise, to hear a fully grown-up Symphonic Rock band (from Poland!) that equaled my favorite rockers. So next to Porcupine Tree this has become my favorite Symphonic Rock Band (Sorry Garbage for the second time).

The 'Second Life Syndrome' album enters my personal top 1000, but who will make the space? The cover is clearly a wink to their western counter parts... Enjoy
